'''班傑明·沃克·戴維斯'''（{{lang-en|Benjamin Walker Davis}}，{{bd|1982年|6月21日}}）<ref name="BW-2009-10-20"/><ref name="BroadwaySpace.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.broadwayspace.com/page/30-under-30-benjamin-walker|title=30 Under 30 - Benjamin Walker|publisher=BroadwaySpace.com|year=2011|quote=Age: 28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830105908/http://www.broadwayspace.com/page/30-under-30-benjamin-walker|archivedate=2011-08-30}}</ref>或簡稱'''班傑明·沃克'''（{{lang-en|Benjamin Walker}}），是一位[[美國|美國]]男演員和[[獨角喜劇|獨角喜劇演員]]。他較著名的是在2012年電影《[[吸血鬼獵人：林肯總統|吸血鬼獵人：林肯總統]]》中擔任主角。此外，他還在廣受好評的音樂劇《[[鐵血總統|鐵血總統]]》中詮釋[[安德魯·傑克森|安德魯·傑克森]]。

==早期生活==
沃克出生於[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]<ref>Brown, Scott. (2010-08-22) [http://nymag.com/guides/fallpreview/2010/theater/67624/ Benjamin Walker on Playing Andrew Jackson in Broadway's 'Bloody, Bloody Andrew Jackson' - Fall Preview 2010] {{Wayback|url=http://nymag.com/guides/fallpreview/2010/theater/67624/ |date=20151211104344 }}, nymag.com; retrieved 2013-08-25.</ref>。母親Jeannine（娘家姓Walker）是一名音樂教師，父親Greg Davis除了擁有一加電影出租店外，還在金融服務業工作<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/17/magazine/benjamin-walker-sexypants-vampire-hunter.html?pagewanted=all|work=The New York Times|first=David|last=Marchese|title=Benjamin Walker, Sexypants Vampire Hunter|date=2012-06-14|accessdate=2015-12-15|archive-date=2014-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811012114/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/06/17/magazine/benjamin-walker-sexypants-vampire-hunter.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Lipworth, Elaine. (2012-06-13) [http://www.metro.co.uk/film/901972-benjamin-walker-meryl-streep-is-an-intimidating-mother-in-law Benjamin Walker: Meryl Streep is an intimidating mother-in-law] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metro.co.uk/film/901972-benjamin-walker-meryl-streep-is-an-intimidating-mother-in-law |date=20121127104906 }}, Metro.co.uk; retrieved 2013-08-25.</ref>。他把母親的娘家姓作為自己的[[藝名|藝名]]，因為[[美國演員工會|美國演員工會]]已經有人先註冊了班傑明·戴維斯<ref name=tms12>{{cite web |url=http://www.times-georgian.com/view/full_story/19028788/article--Abraham-Lincoln--star-has-local-ties?instance=TG_home_story_offset |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130204142842/http://www.times-georgian.com/view/full_story/19028788/article--Abraham-Lincoln--star-has-local-ties?instance=TG_home_story_offset |archivedate=2013-02-04 }}</ref>。他曾就讀過[[卡特斯維爾_(喬治亞州)|卡特斯維爾]]的卡特斯維爾高中、[[特拉弗斯城|特拉弗斯城]]的[[特洛藝術學院|特洛藝術學院]]和[[紐約市|紐約市]]的[[茱莉亞學院|茱莉亞學院]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/6581/benjamin-walker|title=INTERVIEW: Benjamin Walker|publisher=Broadway.com|date=2007-04-19|accessdate=2015-12-15|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222160416/http://www.broadway.com/buzz/6581/benjamin-walker/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年，他從茱莉亞學院的演員培訓計劃畢業<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewarboys.com/content/THE_WAR_BOYS-Press_Notes_Final_4_.pdf|title=The War Boys: Press Notes|format=PDF|accessdate=2011-09-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812160048/http://www.thewarboys.com/content/THE_WAR_BOYS-Press_Notes_Final_4_.pdf|archivedate=2011年8月12日}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
2009年，沃克和[[麥米·古默|麥米·古默]]交往<ref name="BW-2009-10-20">{{cite web | url = http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Mamie_Gummer_Engaged_to_Stage_Actor_Ben_Walker_20091020 | title = Mamie Gummer Engaged to Stage Actor Ben Walker | publisher = BroadwayWorld.com | date = 2009-10-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | archive-date = 2012-10-26 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6BguaVJcU?url=http://broadwayworld.com/article/Mamie-Gummer-Engaged-to-Stage-Actor-Ben-Walker-20091020 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並在2011年結婚<ref>{{cite web | url = http://news-briefs.ew.com/2011/07/20/mamie-gummer-marries/ | title = Meryl Streep's daughter Mamie Gummer marries | publisher = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2011-07-20 | accessdate = 2015-12-15 | archive-date = 2012-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120120004938/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2011/07/20/mamie-gummer-marries/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他們住在[[布魯克林|布魯克林]]的[[公園坡|公園坡]]的一個公寓。2013年3月，宣布兩人將友好地分開，並打算離婚<ref>{{cite web|last=Yuan|first=Jada|title=Benjamin Walker Returns to Broadway for Cat on a Hot Tin Roof|url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/01/benjamin-walker-cat-on-a-hot-tin-roof.html|publisher=Vulture.com|accessdate=2013-02-27|date=2013-01-06|archive-date=2013-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213071909/http://www.vulture.com/2013/01/benjamin-walker-cat-on-a-hot-tin-roof.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月，他開始和共同在《[[日月人魚|日月人魚]]》出演的[[凱亞·絲柯黛蘭莉歐|凱亞·絲柯黛蘭莉歐]]約會，於同年12月8日正式在一起<ref>{{cite news|url=http://instagram.com/p/xKzb-6qT4c/|title=The Happiest Woman in the World|date=2014-12-28|work=@kayascods|accessdate=2015-12-15|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117213305/https://instagram.com/p/xKzb-6qT4c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年後期，兩人結了婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/article/benjamin-walker-kaya-scodelario-married|title=Holiday Wedding! Benjamin Walker and Kaya Scodelario Tie the Knot|last=Guglielmi|first=Jodi|date=2016-01-08|publisher=People|accessdate=2016-06-20|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520032617/http://www.people.com/article/benjamin-walker-kaya-scodelario-married|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年6月7日，宣布他們正期待著兩人第一個小孩的到來<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BGW51WBi9FF/?taken-by=findthewalker|title=Instagram photo by Ben Walker Scodelario-Davis • Jun 7, 2016 at 3:13pm UTC|website=Instagram|access-date=2016-06-07}}</ref>。

